VITE_API_URL=https://portfolio-backend-rfcm.onrender.com/api
```
Leave the actual URL as placeholder for now — we'll update after deploying backend.

### 3 — Make sure both `.gitignore` files have `.env`
In `backend/.gitignore` make sure these exist:
```
.env
dist/
node_modules/
```

In `frontend/.gitignore`:
```
.env
.env.production
node_modules/
dist/